":"If `checkCoeffDvd` is `true`, then when using a polynomial `k*m - p`\nto simplify `.. + k'*m*m_2 + ...`, the substitution is performed IF\n- `k` divides `k'`, OR\n- Ring implements `NoNatZeroDivisors`.\n\nWe need this check when simplifying disequalities. In this case, if we perform\nthe simplification anyway, we may end up with a proof that `k * q = 0`, but\nwe cannot deduce `q = 0` since the ring does not implement `NoNatZeroDivisors`\nSee comment at `PolyDerivation`.\n\nWe also need it when destructively simplifying equations, i.e., when *replacing* an\nequation with its simplified form (`EqCnstr.simplify` and `EqCnstr.simplifyBasis`):\nthe rewrite multiplies the equation by `k₁ = k/gcd k k'`, and the result is weaker than\nthe original equation when `k₁ ≠ ±1`. See **Note** at `EqCnstr.simplify`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.checkCoeffDvd","kind":"def","line":48,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.checkCoeffDvd","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.lean#L48-L48"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.ringId\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">CommRing</span>.<span class=\"name\">RingM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">ringId</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.ringId","kind":"def","line":31,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.ringId","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.lean#L31-L31"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">CommRing</span>.<span class=\"name\">RingM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context\">Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.mk","kind":"ctor","line":30,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.lean#L30-L48"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">CommRing</span>.<span class=\"name\">RingM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context","kind":"structure","line":30,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.RingM.Context","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.lean#L30-L48"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.incSteps\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">CommRing</span>.<span class=\"name\">incSteps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> := <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.incSteps","kind":"def","line":27,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.CommRing.incSteps","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/CommRing/RingM.lean#L27-L28"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" hr